---
title: Pan-fried Chicken in Sage Butter with roasted aubergine and sweet potato mash
description: Though this dish has a lot of enticing elements, the standout may just be the sage butter that bastes the juicy chicken. Sage is a herb with a powerful and distinctive taste, but it's also packed with vitamins A and C as well as even more antioxidants!
